#eNCA's Heidi Giokos reports. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG  eNCA's Heidi Giokos has spent the morning out and about in Johannesburg, monitoring the traffic. She caught up with JMPD spokesperson Xolani Fihla says the city is working to remove unqualified people manning robots that aren't working at various intersections. He says the risk of having them there is too high.